name: I LOVE YOU MAHAL
tagline: will you still love me in the morning?
body:
### Welcome to our page.
Maging positive ka lang mahal, kaya natin to whatever trials ma encounter i hope that we stay strong and still love each other. Mahal na mahal kita.
